About JobAdder  
**   
JobAdder is an innovative B2B, cloud-based SaaS recruitment CRM and ATS
designed to help make recruiting more efficient and joyful for everyone. We
put people at the centre of the recruitment process, liberate recruitment
professionals from unnecessary admin, and empower them to focus on building a
rich and rewarding experience for candidates, clients, and colleagues alike.  
  
With Seek as our parent company, we are fortunate to have access to a broad
range of multinational resources whilst still maintaining our unique identity
and the ability to make quick decisions.  
  
We have over 200 staff globally, with headquarters in Sydney and staff in the
UK, North America and New Zealand.  
  
All of our people actively contribute to our culture and company values;  
Empathy, Customer, Innovation, Results. **  
  
  
